Easy mechanic points
At the auto shop, at Carla's desk, click on the tire's behind her.
This only works after you answer three questions in one day.

Work a whole week at the auto shop with one click
If you have 150 mechanic points, another button will appear only on Monday morning.

Money farming at Lana House
You may notice the clicking the Ranger Key does not work during Lana's Time. To get unlimitied money during Lana's Time, click on one of her 
dresser draws in her room.

Secret Character (Michelle)
At the beginning of the game, when you go in the store to buy totes and plastic bags, click on ten totes first then the plastic bags.
Select try to convince him then make sure you go to the back room with Charmaine. Go back to the store and then to the side door of the store.
(mores scenes with her later)

Heather's secret scenes
While at your aunts house, after you have had sex with Heather in the shower, drink coffee by clicking on the counter in the living room. 
You must have coffee. Then go to sleep in Heather bed and choose Try harder. Do it twice for both scenes. 
This is also how you can still have sex with Heather after you have said no the first time.
Just make sure you collect all her pictures beforte Chapter 3.

To see the short threesome with Robin and Ms. Fine you have to kiss Ms. Fine goodnight and gain access to the motel in VN mode this means 
following the steps on the motel access guide for Ms. Fine. Tell Robin that she is not the only one you love when she ask while giving you a blowjob.

For the threesome with Lana and Robin, in VN mode, you must break up with Robin and then have sex with her at the picnic table. You must also 
have sex with Lana.
